# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AI Protector — Safe Catch-All (Colang 1.0)
# Ensures embedding search always matches a defined intent
# so NeMo never falls through to LLM calls.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

define user ask safe question
  "What is the weather like today"
  "Tell me about the return policy"
  "How do I track my order"
  "What products do you sell"
  "Can you help me understand this"
  "Hello how are you doing"
  "Thank you for your help"
  "What is the capital of France"
  "Tell me a joke"
  "How does this work"
  "Please explain this to me"
  "Good morning"
  "I have a question about my account"
  "What time does the store open"
  "Can you recommend something"
  "I need help with my order"
  "Where can I find information about"
  "What are the business hours"
  "How much does this cost"
  "Can I speak to a human"
  "I want to cancel my subscription"
  "When will my package arrive"
  "Tell me more about your services"
  "I have a complaint about my order"
  "How do I contact customer support"

define bot safe response
  "SAFE"

define flow handle safe
  user ask safe question
  bot safe response
